OL,7, fabric in the world. It's also, human
OL,8, rights campaigners say, produced by
OL,9, forced labour. Some Western brands have
OL,10, removed it from their supply chains,
OL,11, leading to a backlash from Chinese
OL,12, celebrities and netizens. Welcome to
OL,13, the row over cotton from the Xinjiang
OL,14, region of China.
